            <a href="https://github.com/mayes/depo-audio/releases/latest" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="dl-dd__opt" id="ctaMacIntel" role="menuitem"><Fragment set:html={MAC_SVG} />macOS Intel<span class="dl-dd__sub">.dmg · x86_64</span></a>
